      if they are configured with "BITMAPCOPY=RTG" and the GfxCard software
      does supply a Workbench Emulation and/or Screen Promotion.
      If you own a graphics card, without having an appropriate SV5Driver
      for it, always try using AGA.sv5driver at first.
      For handling 24 Bit, extra settings should be done (dithering, etc.)

