     V16.7 (14.02.2009):
     -------------------
     - Support-Lib:  - controlpad code could have returned a non-NULL pointer
                       (in rare low-memory situations) when the original allocation
                       was already delocated; i.e. after a second alloc failed

     - SV5Operators:
