                     - RAW-META:   - subtypes now listed as "(Meta/...")
                                     instead of just "..."
                                   - added new sub-type "Text"
                                     which exports textual meta
                                     tags as text (which tag is
                                     exported depends on controlpad
                                     settings)
                                   - fixed error codes

                     - RAW-IMPORT: - fixed docs
                                   - fixed info text
                                   - optimized options parsing

                     - DEEP:       - no longer rejects 48 bit files
                                     on saving
                                   - fixed metadata memleak

                     - RGB8:       - fixed metadata memleak

                     - ILBM:       - fixed metadata memleak

                     - YUVN:       - fixed metadata memleak

                     - PBM:        - fixed metadata memleak

                     - ACBM:       - fixed metadata memleak

                     - FAXX:       - fixed metadata memleak

     - SV5Operators:
                     - _ALL_ SV5Operators:

                                   - fixed return codes for rejection
                                     of unsupported buffer types;
                                     so that e.g. SView5 can take
                                     necessary means for auto-conversion

