                                    in saver

     V10.8 (17.2.2007):
     -----------------
     - Installer:    - removed MCP warning, since not tested/verified
                       since ages anymore (obsolete?)

     - Support-Lib:  - MOS .elf module was missing in the release
                       archive since the very beginning (oops)

     - SV5Operators: - Convolve:  - added 8 more 3x3 filters
                                  - including Darken 25, Lighten 25
                                    and Negative
                                  - also Nightshift 25/50 are very(!)
                                    nice effects
                                  - Edge_Laplace12 is also good
                                  - totally 49 filters now
                                  - fixed description string

                     - ConvolveNxN:
                                  - added 7 more 5x5 filters
                                  - including Darken 25%, Lighten 25%
                                    and Negative
                                  - totally 21 filters now
                                  - fixed version & description string

                     - ConvolveFloat:
                                  - NEWLY added
                                  - 3x3 convolution matrix floating point
                                    operator
                                  - allows for using matrix coefficients
                                    like 1/3 (0.3333333)
                                  - in most cases this is not required,
                                    but for some special matrices it is
                                    useful
                                  - totally 10 filters included so far

                     - Blur:      - due to a bug in the build script,
                                    the 68030 versions was previously
                                    missing in the release archive
                                  - added 040 version
                                  - fixed some FFP-related compile switches

                     - Sharpen:   - due to a bug in the build script,
                                    the 68030/040 versions were previously
                                    missing in the release archive

                     - Resize:    - added 040 version
                                  - make better use of optimizer

                     - 24BitToHAM:
                                  - added 040 version
                                  - make better use of optimizer

                     - EdgeDetect:
                                  - make better use of optimizer

                     - AlphaBlend:
                                  - added 030 and 040 version
                                  - make better use of optimizer

                     - FixAlphaBlend:
                                  - added 030 and 040 version
                                  - make better use of optimizer

     - SV5Objects:   - PCD:       - added 040 version
                                  - here, the 040 version really
                                    differs significantly even
                                    in size (lots of mulus)


