     V10.5 (10.2.2007):
     -----------------

     - Docs:         - release date of v10.4 actually was 9.2. (fixed)
                     - fixed .guide node (PREFERENCES)
                       (-> Roland Heyder)

     - SV5Operators: - Sharpen:   - removed optional controlpad setting
                                    (-> Roland Heyder)

                     - Convolve:  - new .cpinfo file was missing in
