     V10.4 (9.2.2007):
     -----------------

     - Docs:         - added missing .guide link for new Ghost SV5Operator,
                       also fixed v10.3 version history

     - SV5Operators: - Convolve:  - fixed borders
                                  - slightly optimized
                                  - added 040 version

                     - Sharpen:   - fixed borders
                                  - slightly optimized
                                  - added 040 version

                     - ScaleFree: - added 040 version

                     - EdgeDetect:
                                  - fixed borders
                                  - changed matrix
                                  - slightly optimized
                                  - added 040 version

                     - ConvolveNxN:
                                  - NEWLY added ConvolveNxN operator
                                    which works similar to Convolve,
                                    but allows to dynamically switch
                                    between a 5x5, 7x7 and 9x9 matrix
