                                  - optimized
                     - RGFX:      - reading uncompressed files did not work;
                                    always returned "no graphics data found"
                                  - fixed config parsing (xpkmethod)
                     - UltraConv: - more efficient file type checking
                     - UtahRLE:   - now finally disabled, since
                                    obsolete;
                                    while still physically present,
                                    it is de-facto inactive;
                                    if you need the functionality,
                                    use a datatype
                     - XWD:       - added to main distribution archive
                                  - applied previously missing fixes

      - SVOperators: - ALL:           - improved NULL protection
                     - AlphaBlend:    - now uses "local" settings when calling ScaleFree
                     - DitherFix24:   - optimizations
                     - PaletteDither: - optimizations
                     - EdgeDetect:    - no more IEEE usage
                     - Gamma:         - no more IEEE usage
                     - PagePrint:     - did not work correctly due to wrong OpenLib call;
                                        and wrong reference to AddText
                                      - now uses "local" settings when calling AddTex
                                      - fixed some other bugs; still not in usable state
                     - 24BitToHam:    - slightly optimized

      ...and many more minor fixes


